name: iDream Music "Basic Support" Tee
description:
The iDream Music Basic Classic Support T Shirt is a plain white T Shirt with the "iDream Music" Logo printed on the front. This is the most common shirt you will see at the shows and the only shirts thrown into the crowds. Our cheapest, and most affordable shirt!

NOTE: Shirts are ADULT sizes. If you want a TIGHT fit, order 1 size smaller then you'd normally wear.

name: JoeCat's iDream Music Tee
description: THE official iDream Music T-Shirt designed by JoeCat and SkyLine Printing. Shirts fit like "Fruit of the Loom" or "Gildan". Ask me for a shirt in person if you know me. I'll run it by at $10.00.
